      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import random\n",
        "import time\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "def quicksort_non_random(arr):\n",
        "  if len(arr) <= 1:\n",
        "    return arr\n",
        "  first=arr[0]\n",
        "  middle=arr[len(arr)//2]\n",
        "  last=arr[-1]\n",
        "  piv=sorted([first, middle, last])[1]\n",
        "  less=[x for x in arr if x < piv]\n",
        "  greater=[x for x in arr if x > piv]\n",
        "  return quicksort_non_random(less) + [piv] + quicksort_non_random(greater)\n",
        "\n",
        "def quicksort_random(arr):\n",
        "  if len(arr) <= 1:\n",
        "    return arr\n",
        "  piv=random.choice(arr)\n",
        "  less=[x for x in arr if x < piv]\n",
        "  greater=[x for x in arr if x>piv]\n",
        "  return quicksort_random(less)+[piv]+quicksort_random(greater)\n",
        "\n",
        "def best_case(n):\n",
        "  return list(range(n))\n",
        "\n",
        "def worst_case(n):\n",
        "  return list(range(n, 0, -1))\n",
        "\n",
        "def average_case(n):\n",
        "  return [random.randint(0, n) for _ in range(n)]\n",
        "\n",
        "def benchmark():\n",
        "  sizes=[10, 100, 1000, 10000]\n",
        "  results={'best': [], 'worst': [], 'average': []}\n",
        "  for n in sizes:\n",
        "    start=time.time()\n",
        "    quicksort_non_random(best_case(n))\n",
        "    results['best'].append(time.time() - start)\n",
        "\n",
        "    start=time.time()\n",
        "    quicksort_non_random(worst_case(n))\n",
        "    results['worst'].append(time.time() - start)\n",
        "\n",
        "    start=time.time()\n",
        "    quicksort_non_random(average_case(n))\n",
        "    results['average'].append(time.time() - start)\n",
        "\n",
        "  return results, sizes\n",
        "\n",
        "# Plotting the results\n",
        "def plot_results(results, sizes):\n",
        "  plt.plot(sizes, results['best'], label='Best Case', marker='o')\n",
        "  plt.plot(sizes, results['worst'], label='Worst Case', marker='o')\n",
        "  plt.plot(sizes, results['average'], label='Average Case', marker='o')\n",
        "  plt.xlabel('Input Size (n)')\n",
        "  plt.ylabel('Time (seconds)')\n",
        "  plt.title('Quicksort Benchmarking (Non-Random Pivot)')\n",
        "  plt.legend()\n",
        "  plt.grid()\n",
        "  plt.show()\n",
        "\n",
        "if __name__ == \"__main__\":\n",
        "  results, sizes = benchmark()\n",
        "  plot_results(results, sizes)\n",
        ""
